# Waitlist provider for /api/notify. Set ONE of the options below, then copy
# this file to .env.local (dev) or add the vars in your host's dashboard (prod).
# With nothing set, dev logs signups and succeeds; production returns 503.

# Option A — generic webhook (simplest). Point at a Google Apps Script web app,
# a Zapier/Make catch hook, Formspree, n8n, etc. Receives {email, ts, source}.
WAITLIST_WEBHOOK_URL=

# Option B — email each signup to yourself via Resend (https://resend.com).
# RESEND_API_KEY=
# WAITLIST_NOTIFY_EMAIL=you@studio.com
# WAITLIST_FROM_EMAIL=Palma <onboarding@resend.dev>
